   "source": [
    "# Model Improvement & Calibration — Week 4\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook digs into:\n",
    "1. **Misclassification analysis** — why does the model get certain games wrong?\n",
    "2. **Calibration comparison** — Platt (sigmoid) vs Isotonic vs uncalibrated\n",
    "3. **Reliability diagrams** — before and after calibration\n",
    "4. **Feature experiment** — do interaction features improve accuracy?\n",
    "5. **Final improved model assessment**"
   ]
  },
